Monogame 3.2 allows construction and modification to class SongCollection. This is now changed in latest dev. Here is code that works in 3.2:

  Songs =  new Microsoft.Xna.Framework.Media.SongCollection();

Songs.Add((Song)item.Value);

Latest dev build 1/2/2015 throws this error:

Error   2   The type 'Microsoft.Xna.Framework.Media.SongCollection' has no constructors defined
